SDominanceRelationImpl
public interface SDominanceRelation
extends STextOverlappingRelation, STimeOverlappingRelation

A representation of the model object 'SDominance Relation'.

The following features are supported:

  • SStructure
  • SStructured Target
  • SDocument Graph
